Dear leachers,
I am glad that so many of you are showing the interest for the torrent, but if you are not seeding even little after you got your 100% this torrent will die.
I have a fast connection and I understand that you might be able to download much before you reach your 1-1 ratio. Nevertheless, think of all the others that want this show as much as you do, andt han think that I don't have unlimited place on my HD. Just one extra day after you got your 100 %  is all that is asked from each and every one of you.
So, please, share the joy. Be generous. I know, somewhere, deep down, inside, most of you are compassionate and very well brought up people :)

Greetings

/Mimimae
This went pretty fast for a while then it just stopped, I see there are 60 leechers and only 25 of us seeding. :(
